# ARC Functional Personas

## 1. Operational User (Logger)
Role scope: high-speed intake and shift-start call-out logging.

Workflow requirements:
- Search by Employee ID, First Name, or Last Name.
- If employee is missing, prompt immediate add-new flow.
- `Recorded By` and verification modal are mandatory before save.
- Historical notes are read-only.
- Intake page should be uncluttered (no redundant `Logger Console` title).

## 2. Data Administrator (IT/Admin)
Role scope: data integrity and system maintenance.

Workflow requirements:
- Access and correct data directly in SQLite using SQL tools.
- Bulk-import employee roster data (CSV/Excel source) to maintain search accuracy.
- Monitor `error_log.txt` for runtime DB/access issues.

## 3. Analytical User (Reporting)
Role scope: attendance trend analysis and staffing support.

Workflow requirements:
- View Top 10 High-Frequency report on a dedicated Reporting screen.
- Pull individual employee audit history.
- Optional: export/copy report output for shift handover communication.
